006package dev.metaschema.oscal.tools.cli.core.commands;
007
008import edu.umd.cs.findbugs.annotations.NonNull;
009
010/**
011 * A CLI command that supports resolving an OSCAL profile into a resolved
012 * catalog.
013 */
014public class ResolveCommand
015    extends AbstractResolveCommand {
016
017  @NonNull
018  private static final String COMMAND = "resolve-profile";
019
020  @Override
021  public String getName() {
022    return COMMAND;
023  }
024}
